00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:36.340 align:middle line:84%
The theme of my campaign is to
fulfill the dream, a campaign

00:15:36.340 --> 00:15:38.560 align:middle line:90%
for a positive future.

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:45.010 align:middle line:84%
In 1776, our forbearers freed
the individual from the tyranny

00:15:45.010 --> 00:15:47.220 align:middle line:90%
of the divine right of kings.

00:15:47.220 --> 00:15:49.390 align:middle line:84%
They stated the
self-evident truth

00:15:49.390 --> 00:15:52.080 align:middle line:84%
that all men are
created equal when there

00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:55.210 align:middle line:90%
was no equality in the world.

00:15:55.210 --> 00:16:00.830 align:middle line:84%
There were kings and subjects,
classes and races, sexism.

00:16:00.830 --> 00:16:05.700 align:middle line:84%
Yet the power of the word
of truth changed the world.

00:16:05.700 --> 00:16:09.970 align:middle line:84%
In 1984, we face a tyranny
far greater than King George.

00:16:09.970 --> 00:16:12.760 align:middle line:84%
And we are seeking a
freedom even greater

00:16:12.760 --> 00:16:14.930 align:middle line:90%
than that of the individual.

00:16:14.930 --> 00:16:18.820 align:middle line:84%
The tyranny we face is the
threat of the extinction

00:16:18.820 --> 00:16:21.590 align:middle line:90%
of the human race.

00:16:21.590 --> 00:16:24.060 align:middle line:10%
And the freedom we seek
is the emancipation

00:16:24.060 --> 00:16:27.630 align:middle line:10%
of the genius of the
human race to fulfill

00:16:27.630 --> 00:16:29.570 align:middle line:10%
our highest potential.

00:16:29.570 --> 00:16:34.170 align:middle line:10%
In 1984, we must state
the new self-evident truth

00:16:34.170 --> 00:16:38.160 align:middle line:10%
from the point of power of
the American presidency.

00:16:38.160 --> 00:16:43.940 align:middle line:10%
And the power of this word will
transform the world once again.

00:16:43.940 --> 00:16:48.150 align:middle line:10%
The new truth is that
we are one planet.

00:16:48.150 --> 00:16:51.190 align:middle line:90%
We are one peoples of the Earth.

00:16:51.190 --> 00:16:55.790 align:middle line:84%
And we will live and die
together for evermore.

00:16:55.790 --> 00:17:00.150 align:middle line:84%
It is now in our capacity to
destroy civilization as we know

00:17:00.150 --> 00:17:03.860 align:middle line:84%
it, or to build a world of
unprecedented opportunity

00:17:03.860 --> 00:17:05.058 align:middle line:90%
for all people.

00:17:05.058 --> 00:17:06.349 align:middle line:90%
