00:17:06.349 --> 00:17:09.180 align:middle line:84%
How do you feel watching
that conversation

00:17:09.180 --> 00:17:11.470 align:middle line:90%
20 some odd years ago?

00:17:11.470 --> 00:17:17.369 align:middle line:84%
I feel grateful that I said
yes to that impulse inside me

00:17:17.369 --> 00:17:19.890 align:middle line:90%
to tell the grader story.

00:17:19.890 --> 00:17:24.150 align:middle line:84%
And now when I see it,
I realize I was right.

00:17:24.150 --> 00:17:26.790 align:middle line:84%
LISA GARR: Absolutely,
it's the same conversation

00:17:26.790 --> 00:17:28.470 align:middle line:90%
that we are having now.

00:17:28.470 --> 00:17:31.350 align:middle line:84%
It's the same conversation
that people sit in that chair

00:17:31.350 --> 00:17:34.960 align:middle line:84%
and say the same thing
you were saying in 1984.

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:36.850 align:middle line:84%
BARBARA MARX HUBBARD: So
the real story for anybody

00:17:36.850 --> 00:17:39.980 align:middle line:84%
is when you say yes
to the impulse in you

00:17:39.980 --> 00:17:44.554 align:middle line:84%
to express that that yes
is conscious evolution.

00:17:44.554 --> 00:17:45.420 align:middle line:90%
LISA GARR: It's beautiful.

00:17:45.420 --> 00:17:47.750 align:middle line:84%
I mean what you have created
and throughout your story,

00:17:47.750 --> 00:17:52.030 align:middle line:84%
I see the evolution of where you
have come and where we are now.

00:17:52.030 --> 00:17:54.630 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about that
conversation you were having

00:17:54.630 --> 00:17:57.480 align:middle line:90%
in that video on that pulpit.

00:17:57.480 --> 00:18:00.070 align:middle line:84%
You were talking about
creating a new humanity.

00:18:00.070 --> 00:18:04.120 align:middle line:84%
I also need to know why are we
having this same conversation

00:18:04.120 --> 00:18:05.430 align:middle line:90%
28 years later.

00:18:05.430 --> 00:18:08.770 align:middle line:84%
Well, I think that the
crisis of overpopulation,

00:18:08.770 --> 00:18:12.720 align:middle line:84%
pollution, destruction of the
environment has increased.

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:15.110 align:middle line:84%
And now we are aware
of global warming.

00:18:15.110 --> 00:18:17.250 align:middle line:84%
We are aware of
financial difficulties.

00:18:17.250 --> 00:18:19.080 align:middle line:90%
We are aware of terrorism.

00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:22.250 align:middle line:84%
So all of those
awarenesses is in the news

00:18:22.250 --> 00:18:25.350 align:middle line:84%
constantly telling people
that things aren't working.

00:18:25.350 --> 00:18:30.050 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, the need to know what
is working and what is emerging

00:18:30.050 --> 00:18:32.740 align:middle line:84%
is greater than ever before.
-It is.

00:18:32.740 --> 00:18:35.160 align:middle line:84%
But then what are some
of-- I mean, we know this.

00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:36.420 align:middle line:90%
We have this awareness.

00:18:36.420 --> 00:18:38.290 align:middle line:90%
It's all over the place.

00:18:38.290 --> 00:18:40.670 align:middle line:90%
But what are the answers?

00:18:40.670 --> 00:18:41.960 align:middle line:90%
What are the steps?

00:18:41.960 --> 00:18:43.570 align:middle line:90%
What are the solutions?

00:18:43.570 --> 00:18:47.170 align:middle line:84%
I feel that the way
we're going to know

00:18:47.170 --> 00:18:50.100 align:middle line:84%
is by identifying
what's working.

00:18:50.100 --> 00:18:53.620 align:middle line:84%
New health care, what
Gaiam is doing in health.

00:18:53.620 --> 00:18:57.680 align:middle line:84%
All of these things, what
are new spirituality is.

00:18:57.680 --> 00:19:01.630 align:middle line:84%
Where we're bringing the
inner essence of spirit

00:19:01.630 --> 00:19:03.280 align:middle line:90%
in every one of us.

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:05.970 align:middle line:84%
What are the new
economics where we're

00:19:05.970 --> 00:19:07.850 align:middle line:84%
looking for
alternative currencies

00:19:07.850 --> 00:19:09.770 align:middle line:90%
and economic democracy?

00:19:09.770 --> 00:19:13.630 align:middle line:84%
What are the new
possibilities in governance,

00:19:13.630 --> 00:19:15.690 align:middle line:90%
of co-operative management?

00:19:15.690 --> 00:19:17.850 align:middle line:84%
And when you look
for innovations--

00:19:17.850 --> 00:19:21.490 align:middle line:84%
I think of it as a wheel
of co-creation-- in all

00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:23.680 align:middle line:84%
the organic
functions, you'll find

00:19:23.680 --> 00:19:27.830 align:middle line:84%
there's enough that's working
if it were known and connected.

00:19:27.830 --> 00:19:32.880 align:middle line:84%
So I think what we need
to do in 2012 and beyond

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:35.990 align:middle line:84%
is start a global
communication of what's

00:19:35.990 --> 00:19:37.650 align:middle line:90%
working and connected.

00:19:37.650 --> 00:19:40.570 align:middle line:84%
It's exactly what I ran
for vice president for.

00:19:40.570 --> 00:19:42.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, there are a lot of
conversations happening.

00:19:42.790 --> 00:19:46.010 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of small hubs of
conversations and organizations

00:19:46.010 --> 00:19:47.320 align:middle line:84%
that are having
this conversation.

00:19:47.320 --> 00:19:48.960 align:middle line:84%
But I don't see that
they are connected.

00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:50.050 align:middle line:90%
They're not connected.

00:19:50.050 --> 00:19:53.960 align:middle line:84%
And they're not
considered the new news.

00:19:53.960 --> 00:19:59.350 align:middle line:84%
And I am calling for a new
interpretation of the news--

00:19:59.350 --> 00:20:01.580 align:middle line:84%
not what's breaking
down, but what's

00:20:01.580 --> 00:20:04.270 align:middle line:84%
breaking through, in
such a way that you

00:20:04.270 --> 00:20:06.750 align:middle line:90%
see it's a whole system.

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:08.790 align:middle line:84%
Let's say we have a
whole system breaking

00:20:08.790 --> 00:20:11.381 align:middle line:84%
down in environment, in
economics, in health,

00:20:11.381 --> 00:20:13.320 align:middle line:84%
and so forth--
-We hear a lot about that, yes.

00:20:13.320 --> 00:20:15.910 align:middle line:84%
We have a whole system
breaking through.

00:20:15.910 --> 00:20:18.240 align:middle line:84%
Now, that's what
isn't known, even

00:20:18.240 --> 00:20:20.750 align:middle line:84%
though we might know separate
things that might be working.

00:20:20.750 --> 00:20:22.040 align:middle line:84%
LISA GARR: So what
is it specifically?

00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:22.870 align:middle line:90%
What's breaking through?

00:20:22.870 --> 00:20:23.980 align:middle line:90%
What is the good news?

00:20:23.980 --> 00:20:28.340 align:middle line:10%
I would say the good news
is that we are being born

00:20:28.340 --> 00:20:33.190 align:middle line:10%
as a co-evolutionary,
co-creative species in which

00:20:33.190 --> 00:20:38.120 align:middle line:10%
every single person
actually has a creative gift

00:20:38.120 --> 00:20:42.090 align:middle line:10%
that as we say yes
to that, we can

00:20:42.090 --> 00:20:43.830 align:middle line:10%
evolve ourselves personally.

00:20:43.830 --> 00:20:45.670 align:middle line:10%
We can evolve the world.

00:20:45.670 --> 00:20:48.270 align:middle line:84%
And when we connect,
I believe we

00:20:48.270 --> 00:20:52.900 align:middle line:84%
have the technology and
resources to make a world

00:20:52.900 --> 00:20:54.540 align:middle line:90%
that works for everyone.

00:20:54.540 --> 00:20:57.800 align:middle line:84%
I think we can explore
our solar system.

00:20:57.800 --> 00:21:01.380 align:middle line:84%
I think we can evolve
our spirituality.

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:04.860 align:middle line:84%
I think we probably will find
we're in a universe filled

00:21:04.860 --> 00:21:08.220 align:middle line:84%
with life, and
that our crisis is

00:21:08.220 --> 00:21:11.380 align:middle line:84%
the birth not only of
a co-created species

00:21:11.380 --> 00:21:14.350 align:middle line:90%
but of a universal humanity.

00:21:14.350 --> 00:21:18.790 align:middle line:84%
So if you look at little planet
Earth, like the astronauts did,

00:21:18.790 --> 00:21:21.240 align:middle line:90%
you'll see it's a living system.

00:21:21.240 --> 00:21:22.870 align:middle line:90%
It's alive.

00:21:22.870 --> 00:21:25.870 align:middle line:84%
The astronaut saw the
geographical Earth.

00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:30.650 align:middle line:84%
But we're seeing now the people,
the systems, and the connecting

00:21:30.650 --> 00:21:34.430 align:middle line:84%
of the thinking layer through
Facebook, Twitter, Gaiam

00:21:34.430 --> 00:21:38.700 align:middle line:90%
TV, such that here's my vision.

00:21:38.700 --> 00:21:42.420 align:middle line:84%
That there's enough input
into that collective nervous

00:21:42.420 --> 00:21:45.630 align:middle line:84%
communication system,
like the nervous system

00:21:45.630 --> 00:21:48.310 align:middle line:90%
of a newborn baby.

00:21:48.310 --> 00:21:50.510 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't know it's been born.

00:21:50.510 --> 00:21:52.650 align:middle line:90%
It needs its mother's love.

00:21:52.650 --> 00:21:55.320 align:middle line:84%
It goes against the loving
heart of the mother.

00:21:55.320 --> 00:21:56.800 align:middle line:90%
It hears that heartbeat.

00:21:56.800 --> 00:21:59.880 align:middle line:90%
And its nervous system links up.

00:21:59.880 --> 00:22:02.830 align:middle line:90%
It opens its eyes and smiles.

00:22:02.830 --> 00:22:05.790 align:middle line:84%
I see that this nervous
system, now filled

00:22:05.790 --> 00:22:10.340 align:middle line:84%
with so many inspirations,
so many projects that work,

00:22:10.340 --> 00:22:14.140 align:middle line:84%
if we have it as the new
news, which I want to do--

00:22:14.140 --> 00:22:18.170 align:middle line:84%
that's my mission now is to
tell the new news of our birth

00:22:18.170 --> 00:22:20.610 align:middle line:84%
as a universal
species and invite

00:22:20.610 --> 00:22:22.510 align:middle line:84%
everybody who has
something that's

00:22:22.510 --> 00:22:24.450 align:middle line:90%
working to tell their story.

00:22:24.450 --> 00:22:27.630 align:middle line:84%
So as I said earlier, that
the way out of this the shift

00:22:27.630 --> 00:22:30.020 align:middle line:84%
and the pain that people maybe
are experiencing right now

00:22:30.020 --> 00:22:31.850 align:middle line:84%
is this a new evolution
and that we're

00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:33.510 align:middle line:90%
in the first phase of this.

00:22:33.510 --> 00:22:35.780 align:middle line:84%
Now you would think where we
are in evolution right now,

00:22:35.780 --> 00:22:38.070 align:middle line:84%
we wouldn't be in a
first phase of anything.

00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:39.750 align:middle line:90%
But you're saying that we are.

00:22:39.750 --> 00:22:43.990 align:middle line:84%
Yes, we're the first phase of
a species that could destroy

00:22:43.990 --> 00:22:46.730 align:middle line:84%
its own environment
and knows it,

00:22:46.730 --> 00:22:50.110 align:middle line:84%
and that could evolve its
own, not only environment,

00:22:50.110 --> 00:22:53.510 align:middle line:84%
personal, social,
technological, such

00:22:53.510 --> 00:22:55.420 align:middle line:84%
that we could
transcend what we've

00:22:55.420 --> 00:22:58.880 align:middle line:90%
known as the human existence.

00:22:58.880 --> 00:23:03.720 align:middle line:84%
We have gained powers we
used to attribute to gods.

00:23:03.720 --> 00:23:07.390 align:middle line:84%
So I feel symbolically
that we have

00:23:07.390 --> 00:23:10.570 align:middle line:84%
to recognize that the
design of creation

00:23:10.570 --> 00:23:15.670 align:middle line:84%
is to create people who are
co-creators with the process

00:23:15.670 --> 00:23:16.380 align:middle line:90%
of creation.

00:23:16.380 --> 00:23:18.900 align:middle line:90%
We're meant to have this power.

00:23:18.900 --> 00:23:24.010 align:middle line:84%
But it won't be guided from
the existing structures

00:23:24.010 --> 00:23:28.790 align:middle line:84%
of global corporations,
existing organized religions,

00:23:28.790 --> 00:23:30.040 align:middle line:90%
top down structures.

00:23:30.040 --> 00:23:32.280 align:middle line:90%
Who is it going to be guided by?

00:23:32.280 --> 00:23:35.360 align:middle line:84%
The people who are
connecting like you and me.

00:23:35.360 --> 00:23:37.820 align:middle line:84%
We're not the head
of a nation state.

00:23:37.820 --> 00:23:40.140 align:middle line:84%
We're not the head of
a global corporation.

00:23:40.140 --> 00:23:41.230 align:middle line:90%
Who are we?

00:23:41.230 --> 00:23:41.930 align:middle line:90%
We're the people.

00:23:41.930 --> 00:23:43.500 align:middle line:90%
Who is listening to this?

00:23:43.500 --> 00:23:44.330 align:middle line:90%
The people.

00:23:44.330 --> 00:23:45.480 align:middle line:90%
Those are the ones.

00:23:45.480 --> 00:23:47.170 align:middle line:90%
We have the internet.

00:23:47.170 --> 00:23:54.450 align:middle line:84%
And Birth 2012, December 22,
2012 is being designed as a day

00:23:54.450 --> 00:23:56.110 align:middle line:90%
to celebrate what's working.

00:23:56.110 --> 00:24:00.160 align:middle line:84%
So December 22, that the
day after the alleged date

00:24:00.160 --> 00:24:03.680 align:middle line:84%
of December 21, Birth 2012,
what do you mean by that?

00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:08.190 align:middle line:84%
What I mean is that it's
time to celebrate everything

00:24:08.190 --> 00:24:12.700 align:middle line:84%
that can that we feel is working
toward a more positive future.

00:24:12.700 --> 00:24:17.610 align:middle line:84%
It's a time on a planetary scale
to connect through the heart.

00:24:17.610 --> 00:24:20.690 align:middle line:84%
We're calling it
Heart Coherence.

00:24:20.690 --> 00:24:27.210 align:middle line:84%
And it is said that if 350,000
people simultaneously felt love

00:24:27.210 --> 00:24:30.500 align:middle line:84%
in their heart for each
other and for all species

00:24:30.500 --> 00:24:31.620 align:middle line:90%
and for the planet--

00:24:31.620 --> 00:24:32.710 align:middle line:90%
At the same time?

00:24:32.710 --> 00:24:35.090 align:middle line:84%
At the same time,
it would shift

00:24:35.090 --> 00:24:38.630 align:middle line:90%
that consciousness of Earth.

00:24:38.630 --> 00:24:43.320 align:middle line:84%
And for me Birth 2012, and
beyond-- but just take it

00:24:43.320 --> 00:24:47.140 align:middle line:84%
as a marker-- is a time to
connect through the heart,

00:24:47.140 --> 00:24:52.540 align:middle line:84%
to celebrate what works, and
to have a shared intention

00:24:52.540 --> 00:24:56.250 align:middle line:84%
of a consciousness shift
on planet Earth in time

00:24:56.250 --> 00:24:58.720 align:middle line:84%
to save us from
more destruction.

00:24:58.720 --> 00:25:01.310 align:middle line:84%
So this conversation is
obviously already happening.

00:25:01.310 --> 00:25:02.550 align:middle line:90%
This is happening now.

00:25:02.550 --> 00:25:04.630 align:middle line:84%
It'll happen beyond
the December date.

00:25:04.630 --> 00:25:06.380 align:middle line:84%
This conversation
is in play right

00:25:06.380 --> 00:25:09.280 align:middle line:90%
now, this new conversation.

00:25:09.280 --> 00:25:11.440 align:middle line:84%
The new conversation
is in play.

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:15.120 align:middle line:84%
But because the mass
media and the news system

00:25:15.120 --> 00:25:16.940 align:middle line:84%
and the existing
political system

00:25:16.940 --> 00:25:21.220 align:middle line:84%
doesn't pick up the
news of what's emerging.

00:25:21.220 --> 00:25:23.030 align:middle line:84%
Well, actually, it
shows that there's

00:25:23.030 --> 00:25:24.940 align:middle line:90%
more opposing forces than ever.

00:25:24.940 --> 00:25:27.740 align:middle line:84%
I mean, do you think that
it's become even more apparent

00:25:27.740 --> 00:25:30.040 align:middle line:84%
that the news and
the devastation

00:25:30.040 --> 00:25:34.720 align:middle line:84%
is getting louder as this
conversation gets louder?

00:25:34.720 --> 00:25:38.300 align:middle line:84%
In some respects, the
purpose of getting all of that

00:25:38.300 --> 00:25:40.830 align:middle line:90%
break down news is to awaken.

00:25:40.830 --> 00:25:42.940 align:middle line:84%
But we have to be
careful not to become

00:25:42.940 --> 00:25:46.560 align:middle line:84%
so disappointed or
fearful that we don't

00:25:46.560 --> 00:25:49.110 align:middle line:90%
listen to that inner impulse.

00:25:49.110 --> 00:25:50.860 align:middle line:84%
And what I have
learned personally

00:25:50.860 --> 00:25:54.020 align:middle line:84%
from being a mother of five
and going through all of this

00:25:54.020 --> 00:26:00.160 align:middle line:84%
is when you have what I call
vocational arousal, when

00:26:00.160 --> 00:26:04.890 align:middle line:84%
something excites you to
express, instead of saying,

00:26:04.890 --> 00:26:06.390 align:middle line:84%
well, I don't think
I'm good enough,

00:26:06.390 --> 00:26:11.780 align:middle line:84%
say, yes, knowing it's the
impulse of evolution in you.

00:26:11.780 --> 00:26:15.100 align:middle line:84%
And when anyone, but
particularly a woman,

00:26:15.100 --> 00:26:19.924 align:middle line:84%
says yes to that impulse,
as she gets older, 50, 60,

00:26:19.924 --> 00:26:25.560 align:middle line:84%
70-- I'm 82-- when she
gets older and says,

00:26:25.560 --> 00:26:30.580 align:middle line:84%
yes, instead of aging and losing
vitality, what's happening

00:26:30.580 --> 00:26:36.360 align:middle line:84%
is we're awakening to more
creativity and so are the men.

00:26:36.360 --> 00:26:40.970 align:middle line:84%
They are no longer needing to
be in a dominator position,

00:26:40.970 --> 00:26:44.840 align:middle line:84%
men start tuning in to their
essence, to their creativity.

00:26:44.840 --> 00:26:47.170 align:middle line:90%
And that's the new partnership.

00:26:47.170 --> 00:26:49.460 align:middle line:90%
This is the new partnership.

00:26:49.460 --> 00:26:51.900 align:middle line:90%
This is conscious evolution.

00:26:51.900 --> 00:26:54.460 align:middle line:84%
This is what it means to
be an evolutionary human.

00:26:54.460 --> 00:26:55.690 align:middle line:84%
We're going to
take a quick break

00:26:55.690 --> 00:26:58.474 align:middle line:84%
and be right back with
Barbara Marx Hubbard.

